{
  "stem": "19111.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 199.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Excuse me, in 19-- 1940--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I'm talking about that one point, before they-- actually, the Vilna ghetto at one point was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in 1940.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I believe it was June of 1943.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, gradually--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this is part of what happened, see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The people in Kailis remained after the liquidation of the ghetto The ghetto was liquidated in June of 1943, and Kailis maintained until June of 1944.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Remained, rather, there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, what happened there, at one point the Germans made an announcement in Kailis that all the mothers and the children are to be taken.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Across the street was some kind of a hospital, a clinic, over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have to be taken there to be inoculated against typhoid-- against typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Typhoid And the men had gone to work, and those who had little babies and those that were up to the age of 15 at the time have to go there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we all went there, Including myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As we came there, as everybody came there, there was another labor camp near us, a smaller of not furriers, but they were mechanics.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They used to refurbish trucks and fixed trucks, and it was called HKP.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't recall exactly what the letters stood for right now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But their children also had to be brought there, and everybody came in there to this hospital, suddenly out of nowhere, the Germans and the Lithuanians came, and they surrounded the entire hospital with machine guns, and stormed in-- into the hospital where all the people were there.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they pulled trucks-- a line of trucks backed up into the doorway, and they started grabbing the children and throwing them onto the trucks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Lithuanians especially were very brutal.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
